name: Never-ending pursuit of breaking news or misleading information presented as news
description:
This is the busy Media Hen, as you can see it's running towards the latest headlines but it’s never gone stop with the massive bullshit happening in our society nowadays. 

Collaboration Art by (10 year old) Oujan X (33 year old) Oujan, yes this piece was 23 years in the making.

UNN0RM4L Artist: Oujan, hand craft design to animation.

UNN0RM4L.Studio collective of less fortunate or non crypto nerd artist that still produce distinctive and brilliant art pieces.

Because the basic knowledge of the #crypto #NFT world is missing, we aim to give them a chance to shine bright and be discovered in this beautiful modern world.

100% going to the artist or their families.
